{"tid":362563,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"孝子求router介紹","createTime":"2017-08-17T04:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T10:05:15.000Z","uid":25986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8cb3edbd78e770c06d587b8dca861c9a3689ce","tid":362563,"uid":25986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"先奉上小弟嘅作品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/121610_40a7bb86f6f4d9e5725ef285dd11de04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F121610_40a7bb86f6f4d9e5725ef285dd11de04.jpg&h=1ef84e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用緊tplink好似係WR940N<br />\n之前router擺係我間房(綠色hi)<br />\n但去到廳已經收唔到<br />\n轉左去紅色位<br />\n就變到廳收得清<br />\n但兩間房+廁所勉強load到youtube1080p片<br />\n有冇router推薦<br />\n等兩間房收清d<br />\n廁所冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672a50b80b8d9e9886931ebe497161a7dc17e603","tid":362563,"uid":37152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"ac88u"},{"pid":"b1294ad55a202d1ca102215569ada84d2fe930c9","tid":362563,"uid":25986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ac88u</blockquote><br />\n1000左右搞唔搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com&d=3dFj3SfxHoqTLguBAiOrbxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ee64f644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">price.com</a> 寫1980<br />\n有d貴"},{"pid":"7fd111eb1bac8c33e6faa332cfa616f39b7878db","tid":362563,"uid":25986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"補hkbn 100mb上網"},{"pid":"c2d12f446376c0d6be8935b5ef6d7f3c22390766","tid":362563,"uid":142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ac88u</blockquote><br />\n1000左右搞唔搞得掂<img src=\"/a